HEADWORD: Architectonical
<hw>Ar`chi*tec*ton"ic*al</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>architectonicus</ets>, Gr. <?/. See
